{"title":"前端-HTML篇","uid":"047e19b2048cebbac54df9d0faf4ab17","slug":"前端-HTML篇","date":"2022-07-06T02:55:50.000Z","updated":"2022-07-06T03:05:04.591Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前端-HTML篇.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"前端-HTML\"><a href=\"#前端-HTML\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前端-HTML\"></a>前端-HTML</h1><p>HTML的全称为<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B6%85%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%B0%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/6972570\">超文本标记语言</a>，是一种<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%B0%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/5964436\">标记语言</a>。它包括一系列<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE/2440469\">标签</a>．通过这些标签可以将网络上的<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/1009768\">文档</a>格式统一，使分散的<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Internet/272794\">Internet</a>资源连接为一个逻辑整体。HTML文本是由HTML命令组成的描述性<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC/5443630\">文本</a>，HTML命令可以说明<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97/612910\">文字</a>，<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2/773307\">图形</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB/206564\">动画</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3/33686\">声音</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC/3371820\">表格</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/2665501\">链接</a>等。</p>\n<h1 id=\"HTML常用标签\"><a href=\"#HTML常用标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HTML常用标签\"></a>HTML常用标签</h1><h3 id=\"Div（盒子）\"><a href=\"#Div（盒子）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Div（盒子）\"></a>Div（盒子）</h3><p><em>特点是独占一行</em>；</p>\n<p>用来布局；</p>\n<p>大盒子</p>\n<h3 id=\"span\"><a href=\"#span\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"span\"></a>span</h3><p>类似一个小合子（跨距），可以跨行显示；</p>\n<p>用来布局</p>\n<h3 id=\"图像标签-img\"><a href=\"#图像标签-img\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"(图像标签:img)\"></a>(图像标签:img)</h3><p><strong>基本格式：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>图像链接（URL）<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-HTML\" data-language=\"HTML\"><code class=\"language-HTML\">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;图像链接（URL）&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;错误，图片无法显示&quot; title&#x3D;&quot;这是一张图片&quot;&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>图像链接（URL）<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>错误，图片无法显示<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>这是一张图片<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">border</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>15<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>src（重点）</strong></p>\n<p>​    是<strong>img</strong>的必要元素，它用于指定图像文件的路径和文件名；可以理解为是图片的属性</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>alt</strong></p>\n<p>​    作用是在图片加载错误时，显示提示文字（替换文本）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>title</strong></p>\n<p>​    标签作用是在鼠标经过或者悬停时，出现文字信息（列如：这是一张图片）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>width</strong></p>\n<p>​    控制图片的宽度（像素）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>heigth</strong></p>\n<p>​    控制图片的宽]高度（像素）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>border</strong></p>\n<p>​    设置图像的边框粗细</p>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong></p>\n<p>​    属性采取键值对的格式，即key=”value”的格式，属性=“属性值”</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>图片标签的路径</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>​    相对路径：</p>\n<p>​                    以引用文件所在位置为参考基础，而建立的目录路径</p>\n<p>​                    <strong>图片相对于HTML页面的位置</strong></p>\n<p>​                    **../**来获取文件位置</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>img.jbg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>img/img.jbg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>​    绝对路径</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>​                        是指目录下的绝对位置，直接到达目标位置，通常是从盘符开始的路径</p>\n<p>​                        *<em>\\*</em>                格式    </p>\n<h3 id=\"超链接标签\"><a href=\"#超链接标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"超链接标签\"></a>超链接标签</h3><p>1.链接的语法格式</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>跳转目标<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>目标窗口弹出方式<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文本或者图像<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>a</strong>-&gt;单词：anchor    意为：锚</p>\n<p><strong>href</strong>：用于指定链接目标的url地址（必须属性）</p>\n<p><strong>target</strong>：用于指定的链接页面的打开方式，其中_self为默认值;  _blank为新窗口中打开方式</p>\n<p>​                <strong>_self</strong> 默认值：当前窗口打开页面（就是本网页刷新一个新页面）</p>\n<p>​                <strong>_blank</strong>:新窗口打开（从新打开一个网页）</p>\n<p><strong>空链接：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">herf</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>目录下同网页名称<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>111<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  //内部链接<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>下载链接</strong>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">herf</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>hexo-theme-matery-pro-master.zip<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>111<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>图片超链接：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">herf</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.baidu.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>img.jbg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>锚点链接：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">herf</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#...<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>11<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>----------<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>...<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"注释：\"><a href=\"#注释：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注释：\"></a>注释：</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>!--</span>      <span class=\"token attr-name\">代码注释</span>    <span class=\"token attr-name\">--!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"特殊字符：\"><a href=\"#特殊字符：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特殊字符：\"></a>特殊字符：</h3><ol>\n<li>空格—————————-&amp;nbsp</li>\n<li>大于号————————-&amp;it</li>\n<li>小于号————————-&amp;gt</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"表格标签：\"><a href=\"#表格标签：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"表格标签：\"></a>表格标签：</h3><p>​    主要用于显示展示数据，并不用来布局！</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  //用于定义表格的标签\n    \n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> //表头标签，文字会居中和加粗，常在第一行显示\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> //定义表格的行，必须嵌套在<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>标签中\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>定义表格的列，必须嵌套在<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>标签中\n            ...\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>align（对齐）</strong> :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>left    左对齐</li>\n<li>center 居中</li>\n<li>right 右对齐</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>border（边框）:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>​          “1”代表有边框</li>\n<li>​           “”默认没有边框</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>cellspadding（文字与边框）:</strong></p>\n<p>​                            规定单元边沿其内容之间的空白，默认1像素；</p>\n<p><strong>cellspacing（单元格和单元格的距离）：</strong></p>\n<p>​                            规定单元格之间的空白，默认2像素；</p>\n<p><strong>width:</strong></p>\n<p>​            规定表格的宽度；</p>\n<p><strong>heigth:</strong></p>\n<p>​            规定表格的高度；</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  //代表-表格的头部\n    \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tbody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>//代表-表格的身体\n    \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tbody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong><thead>内部必须拥有<tr>标签，一般是位于第一行</strong>**</p>\n<p><strong><tbody>主要用于放数据本体</strong></p>\n<p><strong>合并单元格</strong></p>\n<p>跨行合并：<strong>rowspan</strong>=”合并单元格的个数”</p>\n<p>跨列合并：<strong>colspan</strong>=”合并单元格的个数”</p>\n<h3 id=\"列表标签\"><a href=\"#列表标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"列表标签\"></a>列表标签</h3><p><strong>有序列表</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t\t\t\t//与无序列表相同，但有自己的等级\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>无序列表</strong>(重点)</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t\t\t\t//表示无需列表，一般以项目符号呈现表项，里面只能方<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>标签\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t//列表项使用<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>标签定义，里面可以放任意标签，相当于一个容器\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>....<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>无序列表没有等级之分，它们是同级的，无前后之分！</p>\n<p>无序列表会带有自己的样式属性，但在实际使用时，用CSS来控制</p>\n<p><strong>自定义列表</strong>（重点）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t//用于定义描述列表（或者定义列表），与下面两个标签一起用，必须包含下面两个标签\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>名词1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t//<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>和<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>是兄弟关系，不是包含关系，它们没有个数限制\n    //一个<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>可以对应多个<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>名词1解释1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>名词1解释2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>名词1解释3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>自定义列表常用于对术语或者名词进行解释和描述，它没有项目符号!</p>\n<p>类似下面这个样子</p>\n<img src=\"D:\\blog\\source\\_posts\\image-20220510185658559.png\" style=\"zoom: 80%;\" />\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"表单标签\"><a href=\"#表单标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"表单标签\"></a>表单标签</h3><p><strong>作用：</strong>使用表单是为了收集，用户进行交互，收集用户资料！</p>\n<p><strong>构成部分：</strong>“<strong>表单域</strong>”，“<strong>表单控件</strong>”（也称表单元素）和“<strong>提示信息</strong>”，共三个部分。</p>\n<p><img src=\"D:\\blog\\source_posts\\image-20220510191138532.png\" alt=\"image-20220510191138532\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">action</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>url地址<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">method</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>提交方式<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>表单域<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t\n   \n    \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t\t //用于定义表单域，实现收集用户信息并提交给服务器<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"D:\\blog\\source_posts\\image-20220510193422169-16531950665501.png\" alt=\"image-20220510193422169\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>属性</th>\n<th>属性值</th>\n<th>作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>action</td>\n<td>url地址</td>\n<td>用于指定收并处理表单数据的服务器的url地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>method</td>\n<td>get/post</td>\n<td>用于设置表单数据的提交方式，其取值为uget或者post</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>name</td>\n<td>名称</td>\n<td>用于指定表单的名称，以区分同一个页面中的多个表单域</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><strong>表单元素</strong></p>\n<p>​                <strong>input</strong>:输入表单元素</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>属性值<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>选项框名字<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>请输入用户名<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  //单标签\n\n//value属性是告诉后台，数据的类型<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>type-属性值（改变input形态）</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>button</td>\n<td>定义可点击按钮（多数情况下，用于通过js启动脚本）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkbox</td>\n<td>定义复选框</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>file</td>\n<td>定义输入字段和“浏览”按钮，供文件上传</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hidden</td>\n<td>定义隐藏的输入字段</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>image</td>\n<td>定义图像形式的提交按钮</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>password</td>\n<td>定义密码字段，该字段中的字符被掩码（密码框）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>radio</td>\n<td>定义单选按钮,<strong>实现多选一，input属性需要有相同的name值</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>reset</td>\n<td><strong>定义重置按钮。重置按钮会清除表单中的所有数据</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>submit</td>\n<td>定义提交按钮。<strong>提交按钮会把表单数据发送到服务器</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>text</td>\n<td>定义单行的输入字段，用户可在其中输入文字，默认宽度为20个字符</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>input—-属性</th>\n<th>属性值</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>name</td>\n<td>用户自定义</td>\n<td>定义input元素名称<strong>（区别不同的表单元素）</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>value</td>\n<td>用户自定义</td>\n<td>规定input元素的值</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checked</td>\n<td>checked</td>\n<td>规定此input元素首次加载时应当被选中<strong>（页面开始，选项被默认勾选）</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>maxlength</td>\n<td>正整数</td>\n<td>规定输入字段中的字符的最大长度<strong>（输入限制）</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>​                <strong>select</strong>:下拉表单元素</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>选项1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>   //至少包含一对option属性\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>选项2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">selected</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>selected<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>选项3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\t //默认选中\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>选项4<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>​                <strong>textarea</strong>:文本域元素</p>\n<p>用于定义多行文本输入的控件</p>\n<p><strong>rows</strong>属性值代表显示的行数</p>\n<p><strong>cols</strong>属性值代表每行的字符数（实际开发不会使用，都用CSS来修改）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rows</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cols</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>label标签</strong>**</p>\n<p><strong>用于绑定一个表单元素，当点击<label>标签内的文本时，浏览器自动的把光标转贷对应的表单元素</strong></p>\n<p><strong>for属性应当和相关的ID属性相同</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>用户名<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">typr</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>用户名<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","feature":true,"text":"前端-HTMLHTML的全称为超文本标记语言，是一种标记语言。它包括一系列标签．通过这些标签可以将网络上的文档格式统一，使分散的Internet资源连接为一个逻辑整体。HTML文本是由HTML命令组成的描述性文本，HTML命令可以说明文字，图形、动画、声音、表格、链接等。 HTM...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.5k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF-HTML\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前端-HTML</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#HTML%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">HTML常用标签</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Div%EF%BC%88%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Div（盒子）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#span\"><span class=\"toc-text\">span</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE-img\"><span class=\"toc-text\">(图像标签:img)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B6%85%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">超链接标签</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注释：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特殊字符：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">表格标签：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">列表标签</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A1%A8%E5%8D%95%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">表单标签</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"前端-CSS篇","uid":"406443983bf20edb3c85196d5fc66800","slug":"前端-CSS篇","date":"2022-07-06T02:58:47.000Z","updated":"2022-07-06T03:05:31.180Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前端-CSS篇.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"前端-CSSCSS简介也叫层叠样式表（Cascading Style Sheets） 它是一种标记语言 美化网页，重要用来布局（文本内容，图片的外形，版面的外观显示样式） 层叠样式表(英文全称：Cascading Style Sheets)是一种用来表现HTML（标准通用标记语言...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.9k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{}}